@startuml
title Activity Diagram: Create New Project

|User|
start
:Click "Create New Project";
:Enter project name;
:Enter project description\n(optional);
:Click "Create" button;

|System|
:Validate inputs;
if (Name is empty?) then (yes)
  |User|
  :Show error: "Project name is required";
  stop
else (no)
  |System|
  :Create project in MongoDB;
  :Generate project ID;
  |User|
  :Show success message;
  :Redirect to project dashboard;
  stop
endif

@enduml

